    "sn56.68:0.1": "Saṁyutta Nikāya 56.68 ",
    "sn56.68:0.2": "7. Paṭhamaāmakadhaññapeyyālavagga ",
    "sn56.68:0.3": "Sāmaññasutta ",
    "sn56.68:1.1": "… “Evameva kho, bhikkhave, appakā te sattā ye sāmaññā; atha kho eteva bahutarā sattā ye asāmaññā …pe…. ",
    "sn56.68:1.2": "Aṭṭhamaṁ. "
  },
